{"tid":769964,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"樹仁係唔係真係好差？","createTime":"2018-08-06T15:16:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T13:33:41.000Z","uid":71302,"like":22,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"92794257904a6173660c42a4b5e853112dde9428","tid":769964,"uid":71302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:16:49.000Z","msg":"今日jupas放榜 我識人no offer<br />\n我叫佢去讀asso/hd博升大學<br />\n佢係都唔肯 要去樹仁/恆管讀 覺得係degree高級d<br />\n我有好多舊同學係asso升u 唔明點解佢係都唔聽<br />\n仲要去讀BBA呢d公廁科 全港間間大學都有BBA<br />\n個競爭咁大 你唔係八大點搵工<br />\n有冇樹仁學生可以講下就業係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6170e393d7fb1ec4430c23ce5aa1fc44cd8eb24","tid":769964,"uid":152520,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:18:10.000Z","msg":"盡人事提咗佢就算啦<br />\n佢要死都冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e24deab6da508af8c4c6857aa903fad81d1007","tid":769964,"uid":166725,"like":14,"dislike":7,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:18:16.000Z","msg":"無知一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實樹仁畢業同中六畢業有咩分別？"},{"pid":"863a0a779bd2b78cc797cd14982a1de8fcd303dd","tid":769964,"uid":192491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:21:09.000Z","msg":"佢要去食屎你都阻唔到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b7fda42d35213acbc5726b72d44dd6eae43fb9","tid":769964,"uid":70817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"佢想死你真係阻唔到"},{"pid":"d193e0177274b86cdc5f1a6ee804dff78c3cc9e2","tid":769964,"uid":166386,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"聽這講入樹仁 毀眾生"},{"pid":"4e6e923062f2b44de5a3587d51854d62f426a33c","tid":769964,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"google下大把post係講treeu幾咁垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2ad093